data.description: This stunning 4 bedroom 3 bath house in Lexington, South Carolina is a must-see! Located in the highly sought after Settlers Pointe at Lake Murray, which offers community dock access. The main level features a full bedroom with a full bathroom, a large dining room and an eat in style kitchen. Cozy up next to the fire place in the huge living room! Upstairs you will find an open loft area which includes the master suite with a dream of a walk in closet and ensuite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and full bath complete the upstairs. Award winning Lexington One schools. Do not let this opportunity pass you by.
